<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Sylvester Stallone's mother Jackie has passed away at the age of 98.</p>

<p>Though the circumstances surrounding the famed astrologer's death remain unknown, sources close to the Stallone family told TMZ that she just 'recently passed away.'</p>

<p>Jackie leaves behind Sylvester, 74, as well as son Frank, 70, whom she shared with late ex husband Frank Stallone Sr. </p>

<p>She is also mother to late actress Toni D'Alto, who passed away at the age of 48 after a lengthy cancer battle in 2012.</p>

